name 'problem-solving-with-ai-postassessment-q1_2025-pilot_v2-2025'

question 'Which of the following is the best way to refine this prompt for a more useful AI response?'

wrong 'Animals exist. Explain them to me.'
wrong 'Tell me everything you know about every animal in the rainforest.'
right 'Tell me three interesting facts about rainforest animals.'
wrong 'Animals are cool. What do you think?'

allow_multiple_attempts true

